      <p>A <a href="ch61s11.html#MonstersB-C63">centaur</a> is as big as a heavy <a href="ch73s21.html#MonstersAnimals68">horse</a>, but much taller and slightly heavier. A <a href="ch61s11.html#MonstersB-C63">centaur</a> is about 7 feet tall and weighs about 2,100 pounds.<a href="img/MonstersB-C.Centaur.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersB-C.Centaur.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <p><a href="ch61s11.html#MonstersB-C63">Centaurs</a> speak Sylvan and Elven.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
